1.1.name: wordpress/funny-video-online
1.1.description: Plugin "Funny video online" displays Funny video on your blog. There are over 10,000 video clips. Add Funny YouTube videos to your sidebar on your blog using a widget. Video are saved on our database, so you don't need to have space for all that information. More WordPress Plugins.
